/*
data types is show that how much the storage it can hold
 
data types      |        format specifiers                  |           examples
                |                                           |
int             |          %d   (whole number)              |     int a=28
float           |          %f   (less precision)            |     float=3.44
double          |          %lf  (more precisiion)           |     double=3.33333
char            |          %c   (single character)          |     char='A'

*/